properties.headline: FLOODING COREEN Riverina Highway CLOSED between Federation Way and Bull Plain Road
properties.diversions:
Eastbound: Bull Plain Rd, Spring Dr and Federation Ave to Corowa, then Honour Ave to return to Riverina Hwy south of Lowesdale.

Westbound: Riverina Hwy and Hounour Ave to Corowa, then Spring Dr and Bull Plain Rd to return to the Riverina Hwy.

This diversion is suitable for all vehicles.

properties.headline: FLOODING DARLINGTON POINT TO COLLINGULLIE Sturt Highway CLOSED between Kidman Way and Lockhart Road
properties.diversions:
Westbound from Wagga Wagga: Olympic Hwy, Coolamon Rd, Canola Way and Newell Hwy to Narrandera. Then, Irrigation Way, Whitton Darlington Point Rd and Kidman Way.

Eastbound from Darlington Point: Kidman Way, Whitton Darlington Point Rd and Irrigation Way to Narrandera. Then, Newell Hwy, Canola Way Coolamon Rd, and Olympic Hwy to Wagga Wagga.

These diversions are suitable for heavy vehicles up to 25/26m B-Double only

Eastbound: Oxley Hwy to Nevertire, Mitchell Hwy to Dubbo, Newell Hwy to Gilgandra.

Westbound: Newell Hwy to Dubbo, Mitchell Highway to Nevertire to the Oxley Highway.

Northbound from Gunnedah: Oxley Hwy to Coonabarabran, Newell Hwy to Narrabri.

Southbound from Narrabri: Newell Hwy to Coonabarabran, Oxley Hwy to Gunnedah.

properties.otherAdvice: Visitors are encouraged to check the Royal National Park local alerts before travelling for updates on precinct access.

Access to/from the Royal National Park is available via Waterfall: Princes Hwy, McKell Av and Sir Bertram Stevens Dr.

From Stanwell Tops: Lawrence Hargrave Dr, Otford Rd, Lady Wakehurst Dr, to access Sir Bertram Stevens Dr.
